     <body>
     <div type="to_the_reader">
   <opener>
      <salute>Courteous Reader,</salute>
   </opener>
   <p> You shal find in this Booke more then was presented upon the <hi>Stage,</hi> and left out of the <hi>Presentation,</hi> for superfluous length (as some of the <hi>Playe<gap reason="illegible" extent="1 letter">
            <desc>•</desc>
         </gap>s</hi> pretended) I thoght good al should be inserted according to the allowed <hi>Original;</hi> and as it was, at first, intended for the <hi>Cock-pit Stage,</hi> in the right of my most deserving Friend Mr. <hi>VVilliam Beeston,</hi> unto whom it properly appertained; and so J leave it to thy perusal, as it was generally applauded, and well acted at <hi>Salisbury Court.</hi>
   </p>
   <closer>
      <signed>Farewell, <hi>Ri. Brome.</hi>
      </signed>
   </closer>
   <trailer>FINIS.</trailer>
   <pb facs="45"/>
</div>
